    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918_2",
    "text": "1.掌握初必背《醉翁亭记》中的重点实词、虚词和句式。 2．感受作者与民同乐的境。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15074566706972994,
      0.21604674362263077,
      0.6658605401047965,
      0.2502493943280604
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918_3",
    "text": "【进作者】",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15638855300282145,
      0.25366965939860336,
      0.2523176138653769,
      0.26906085221604675
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918_4",
    "text": "欧阳修(1007年～1072年)，字永叔，号醉翁，北宋学家，政治家，史学家和诗， “唐宋家”之。因家中有万卷书、千卷遗、张琴、局棋、壶酒、 翁，晚年又号“六居”。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14913341394598953,
      0.2724811172865897,
      0.8520757758968158,
      0.32492518170158186
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_918_5",
    "text": "日",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7593712212817413,
      0.3317657118426678,
      0.8472390165255945,
      0.4132820293572752
    ],
